"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"db341f4877761e6ac5b8ef8c5d9b6b6fc6c5fee7","tid":884304,"uid":83748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"07c5237366e662f52f07d6a3589c8177f15c607c","tid":884304,"uid":154533,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T14:10:35.000Z","msg":"成龍姓陳?"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T14:46:12.000Z","msg":"點解個仔姓房？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T16:12:05.000Z","msg":"因為中國古時分開姓、氏、名、字、號，<br />\n姓的本義是&lsquo;生&rsquo;，是代表有共同血緣、血統、血族關係的種族稱號。<br />\n<br />\n據《春秋》整理的&ldquo;古姓&rdquo;，近半數帶女字旁，所以推測，姓的產生可能在母系氏族社會。<br />\n<br />\n戰國前，貴族才有姓氏，貴族男子稱氏，女子稱姓。因為&ldquo;姓所以別婚姻&rdquo;，&ldquo;氏所以別貴賤&rdquo;，&ldquo;貴者有氏，賤者有名無氏&rdquo;。<br />\n<br />\n正所謂有名有姓，品質保證。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee25d6ad2e9fb44cd188cea950e9b13d73a2fd11","tid":884304,"uid":161649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T16:23:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>下原來成龍姓陳<br />\n我以為佢直接姓成添<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n即係佢全名叫陳成龍？</blockquote><br />\n鬼才 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁都推理得到"},{"pid":"b4bcc1cb81939805b963ad06a0930f6e65f4447e","tid":884304,"uid":146435,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"ee25d6ad2e9fb44cd188cea950e9b13d73a2fd11","tid":884304,"uid":161649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T16:23:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>下原來成龍姓陳<br />\n我以為佢直接姓成添<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n即係佢全名叫陳成龍？</blockquote><br />\n鬼才 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁都推理得到"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T22:57:28.000Z","msg":"只有00後同新移民先唔知成龍姓陳  陳港生係（97前）香港人都知"},{"pid":"4146cc77929f779b8acecc635ce6b567a3717d2a","tid":884304,"uid":55851,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":